All thanks go to Rolando for his work. Artwork is always included.


Lineage:

Trade DVD-R - DVD Decrypter - TLH - maketorrent - ELL


GSpot image is included!


Tracklist:

01 - Keith on the origin of the band' s name
02 - Mick on his blues influences and learning to play harmonica
03 - Keith on his blues heroes, his look and his favorite cover of a Stones' song
04 - Mick on modern rock bands, songs the Stones need to cover and James Brown
05 - Keith on Ron Wood, guitar wearing and the importance of musical white space
06 - Mick on playing bass and listening to reggae and Keith on 'Jumping Jack Flash'
